  "moments": [
    {
      "id": "mo_001",
      "text": "Today was one of those days where everything tiny goes wrong.",
      "tone": "frustrated",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_002",
      "text": "I just want to hit pause and take a deep breath.",
      "tone": "anxious",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_003",
      "text": "I'm learning to laugh at the little mishaps.",
      "tone": "content",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_004",
      "text": "My train delayed, I missed a meeting, and now I'm stuck in this tiny apartment missing the rain.",
      "tone": "frustrated",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-08",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-08",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_005",
      "text": "I wish I could live in that rainy café moment forever — no deadlines, no emails, just chai and a sketchbook.",
      "tone": "hopeful",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-08",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-08",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_006",
      "text": "This chat is saving my rainy evening.",
      "tone": "grateful",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-08",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-08",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_007",
      "text": "It's not loneliness when you're vibing with your favorite tune, right?",
      "tone": "hopeful",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-15",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-15",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_008",
      "text": "It's weird — now I feel less alone.",
      "tone": "grateful",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-15",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-15",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_009",
      "text": "Rare treat, but I chase it like a sunset 🌅. It's that spark that makes the mess worth it.",
      "tone": "hopeful",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-22",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-22",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_010",
      "text": "It's not perfect, but it's *done*.",
      "tone": "content",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-22",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-22",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_011",
      "text": "I'm doing my best. I'm doing my best.",
      "tone": "content",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-22",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-22",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_012",
      "text": "Everything feels heavy — even the smallest comforts feel like work.",
      "tone": "anxious",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-29",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-29",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_013",
      "text": "Just breathing, I guess. Or pretending to.",
      "tone": "anxious",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-29",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-29",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_014",
      "text": "Today I'm still counting ceiling tiles.",
      "tone": "anxious",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-29",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-29",
      "mentions": 1
